data.description: Hard to find brick ranch convenient to I-40/85/shopping/dining with NO HOA. Open-concept living w/fireside great rm adjoining dining & kitchen. Great rm w/hardwoods, smooth ceilings & lighted overhang. Kitchen w/tile, walk-in pantry,  subway backsplash, under-cabinet lights. Master w/HUGE closet, & luxurious bath w/tile floors, soaking tub, separate shower & dual sinks. Updated hall bath, walk-in tile shower. New windows and rear door installed in 2022. New heat and A/C in 2022. New Architectural shingle roof in 2022.  Propane Generac 24kw generator to power entire home in 2022. New 48 gal. Hot water heater in 2022. New Vapor Barrier installed in 2022. Paved driveway/ tinted expoxy driveway,walkway and Covered porch in 2023. Rear deck. New black 6 ft high chain link fenced in back yard in 2022.  ADT monitored Alarm system installed in 2022. New insulation installed under new vinyl siding and new gutters in November 2022. Site-built, wired Dutch Barn also has new roof ,insulation under new siding in 2022. New kitchen sink installed August 2023.
data.whatILove: Home convenient to shopping centers, grocery stores gas stations and restaurants. Convenient to I-85/ I-40 . New dishwasher and kitchen sink installed 2023.
